438
01:06:40.508 --> 01:06:42.052
Homme dans la cabane !

439
01:06:43.678 --> 01:06:44.763
Ted !

440
01:07:03.573 --> 01:07:04.532
Bonjour.

441
01:07:04.574 --> 01:07:05.408
Bonjour.

442
01:07:05.742 --> 01:07:06.618
Belle journée.

443
01:07:08.370 --> 01:07:09.204
Oui.

444
01:07:09.579 --> 01:07:11.957
